\v 20 But \nd Messiah¦119606\nd* has indeed come back to life from the dead¦119609, leading the way for those who have passed away,
\v 21 because¦119615 since¦119614 death¦119619 came through a man \add (Adam)\add*, then the resurrection¦119623 of the dead also comes through a man \add (Yeshua)\add*.
