\v 27 because¦119709 \add (as David wrote)\add*,\x + \xo 15:27: \xt Psa 8:6.\x* ‘God has made everything subject to him.’ (Now when it says ‘everything’, \add of course\add* that doesn't include \add God\add* who's the one that made it happen.)
