\v 57 but¦120216 be thankful¦120218 to \nd God¦120217\nd* because it's him who gives us the victory¦120224 through¦120225 our¦120228 \nd master¦120227 Yeshua¦120229 Messiah¦120230\nd*.
\p
\v 58 Therefore my¦120233 dear brothers¦120232 and sisters¦120232, be strong and stand firm, always¦120246 doing the \nd master's\nd* work enthusiastically, knowing¦120247 that your¦120251 work for \nd Yahweh¦120245\nd* isn't¦120252 wasted.
